      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "When this is the case, the concentration of measure phenomenon leads to the \"canonical typicality\" observed in [CITATION_1] , that is, the fact that \"in the thermodynamic limit, the reduced density matrices of the overwhelming majority of the wave functions of [the system-plus-environment] are canonical.\""
    }
